I wish I'd known about this site BEFORE I went to Indonesia:( I'm sure I would have become an instant fan!

Absolutely love every part of seeing your beautiful photos in my email. Thank you so much!

Amazing!! You are the perfect example of Jack Kerouac....a rockstar who is spreading incredible culture, nature & inspiration!! Many, many thank yous!

This is brilliant. I'm reading it and loving every second of it. How easy to forget what the world might be like if your neighbors don't look like you, speak your language or follow your particular religious beliefs. A fine life left wrought in beautiful pictures tells a marvelous story of the world's people--through your eyes. Thank you.

-An easy life is over rated.Thanx Amir

Incredible photos! I feel fortunate to have been able to see these places through your eyes.

Thanks again! I'm still smiling. Sorry, I feel stupid now, but I even had to google some of the words to, huh yeah, find out what they mean. I just love it!!!

We all love these photos and the things you are teaching us about foods. You are an ambitious person making much of your life. Keep up the great work. We love you!
